<h1>Lorraine's Club Sandwich</h1>
<h2>Ingredients:</h2>
<li>2 slices bacon</li>
<li>3 slices bread, toasted</li>
<li>3 tablespoons mayonnaise</li>
<li>2 leaves lettuce</li>
<li>2 (1 ounce) slices cooked deli turkey breast</li>
<li>2 slices tomato</li>
<h2>Directions:</h2>
<ol>
  <li>Place bacon in a heavy skillet. Cook over medium high heat until evenly brown. Drain on paper towels.</li>
  <li>Spread each slice of bread with mayonnaise. On one slice of toast, place the turkey and lettuce. Cover with a slice of toast, then the bacon and tomato. Top with last slice of toast.</li>
</ol>

